 within the context of one simple fiducial parameterized\nspin distribution, observations favor low BH natal spin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Sep 2017 18:00:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Sep 2017 11:39:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 20 Jun 2018 21:15:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-22"}
