n is triggered by a fluctuation of the magnetic field when\nits amplitude becomes comparable to the field strength in the torus-like outer\nflow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Sep 2017 12:36:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
